#: .\portfolioapp\templates\index.html:168
msgid ""
"A mobile application developed using cross-platform technology, React "
"Native, for a real estate company, Aymen Promotion. The application displays "
"current projects with various flat types and allows users to make virtual "
"visits using 3D modeling. Additionally, users can customize purchased flats, "
"check the building progress, and view daily changes."
msgstr "A mobile application developed using cross-platform technology, React Native, for a real estate company, Aymen Promotion. The application displays current projects with various flat types and allows users to make virtual visits using 3D modeling. Additionally, users can customize purchased flats,  check the building progress, and view daily changes."

#: .\portfolioapp\templates\index.html:189
msgid ""
" A platform we created to display free courses and their coupons, helping "
"people advance in their careers and develop valuable skills."
msgstr "A platform we created to display free courses and their coupons, helping people advance in their careers and develop valuable skills. "

#: .\portfolioapp\templates\index.html:231
msgid ""
"It is a platform that displays real-time data using an API. It presents "
"popular movies, TV shows, and actors, providing details about each. You can "
"find information on movies and TV shows, such as ratings, cast, genre, and "
"trailers. You can access it from the here."
msgstr "It is a platform that displays real-time data using an API. It presents popular movies, TV shows, and actors, providing details about each. You can find information on movies and TV shows, such as ratings, cast, genre, and trailers. You can access it from the here."

#: .\portfolioapp\templates\index.html:251
msgid ""
" Using Django Channels and HTMX, I developed a Django chat application that "
"connects users into groups, enabling real-time messaging with live updates."
msgstr "Using Django Channels and HTMX, I developed a Django chat application that connects users into groups, enabling real-time messaging with live updates."

#: .\portfolioapp\templates\index.html:273
#, python-format
msgid ""
"An AI website based on a TensorFlow-trained model using our AnimAi dataset. "
"We achieved an accuracy of 97%%, and the model is deployed as a web "
"application. The application stores images and displays them along with the "
"results of the prediction."
msgstr "An AI website based on a TensorFlow-trained model using our AnimAi dataset.  We achieved an accuracy of 97%, and the model is deployed as a web application. The application stores images and displays them along with the results of the prediction."
